    "description": "<p>Firstcom Engineering is a Singapore-based engineering and construction company specializing in infrastructural deployment and systems works focusing in train and road tunnels/depots, highways and buidlings.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With over 25 years of experience and a workforce of over 100 employees in Singapore, you will gain hands-on exposure to site operations, project coordination, and technical execution, working closely with experienced installers and project managers. This is an excellent opportunity to build a solid foundation in civil and infrastructure engineering, with structured on-the-job training provided.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With a focus on safety, teamwork, and technical excellence, our mission is to build a strong, future-ready workforce capable of supporting Singapore’s urban development needs. At Firstcom Engineering, we believe in developing our people through hands-on experience, continuous learning, and opportunities for career growth.</p>",
